                <h1>Essential Guide to Forensic Photography</h1>
                <p>Forensic photos are critical in criminal investigations, capturing detailed visual evidence at crime scenes. These images document vital elements such as weapon placements, body positions, and environmental factors, aiding law enforcement and legal processes. Properly taken forensic photographs ensure that no detail is overlooked, providing clarity in court.</p>
